&lt;p&gt;High Up-Front Commissions | Residual Income | Pre-Set Appointments&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you an experienced Merchant Services or B2B outside sales professional who knows how to build relationships, earn trust, and close business?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’ve sold payment processing, POS systems, or business services, this is an opportunity to leverage that experience and build a portfolio that pays you month after month.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are expanding our outside sales team nationwide and looking for proven field sales professionals who want strong up-front commissions and long-term residual income — without the operational headaches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our structure allows you to focus on what matters — getting in front of business owners and closing deals — while our internal teams handle onboarding, implementation, and ongoing merchant support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Experienced Merchant Services Reps Join Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High up-front commissions on every deal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Residual income that grows with every account you board&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualified daily appointments set by our in-house team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Daily commission payouts via direct deposit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Industry-leading payment technology and POS solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dedicated onboarding and merchant support team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;24/7 customer support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Most companies in this industry push service issues back onto the sales rep. We don’t.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our support team handles merchant onboarding and service, so you can spend your time doing what actually makes you money — closing business and building your portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Income Potential&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our top representative earned over $300,000 last year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A consistent producer closing 6–7 deals per month can realistically earn $125K–$200K annually through a combination of up-front commissions and residual income.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who This Is For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced Merchant Services, POS, or B2B outside sales reps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professionals who are comfortable working independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong closers who understand how to build relationships and ask for the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Individuals who want to build and own a long-term book of merchants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
